.mod-tuition
  .layout-inner-wrap
    %h2 Tuition
    %p
      Program tuition is $17,500. A $1000 deposit is needed to secure your spot.
    %p
      Many students elect to defer a portion of their tuition until after they are employed. The first monthly payment is due eight weeks after finishing the program.
    %p
      If you're a right fit for our program we'll do our best to help you afford it. Get accepted first, then we'll worry about the finances.
    %p
      Cost-of-living and housing are not included. Tuition includes a new Apple laptop, but students supplying their own "Mid 2012" or newer MacBook Air or Pro running OS X 10.9 can take a $1200 credit from their up-front payment.

